<headline>Special Weather Statement issued December 23 at 3:28PM EST  by NWS Chicago</headline>
<description>Decreasing visibility can be expected across areas between
Interstate 80 and Interstate 88 through the remainder of the
afternoon. Visibility may be reduced to one quarter mile or less
at times. Motorists should use caution, reduce speed, and increase
following distance.</description>
